{"tid":2426649,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日香港人需毋忘初心","createTime":"2021-02-28T08:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T09:09:21.000Z","uid":393597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee21f0201ee538b7b03174ff8c38e704fe96abdb","tid":2426649,"uid":393597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"這兩年香港發生咁多事，自己客身異鄉升學，就算在呢邊搞幾多次集氣會，幾多次遊行，也只能推到國家向香港開救生艇方案。一直對自己不在港不能與手足們並肩作戰而慚愧。<br />\n<br />\n但我有少少野想講：<br />\n<br />\n今日之後，希望大家可以清楚明白，在香港再沒有抗爭的空間。<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割席，不批鬥，不鬥黃。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，但此刻香港山已無法再爬。<br />\n要走嘅，大家幫佢地走好嗎？<br />\n不要批評，不要鬧人逃兵。<br />\n要理解。<br />\n<br />\n在外地後，香港人都要好好向孫中山先生學習。<br />\n<br />\n他朝一日。<br />\n<br />\n若在外國建立家庭，一定要好好教育我們的下一代。<br />\n<br />\n要教我們的子女講廣東話、要教佢地寫中文、要教佢地香港人嘅歷史與共產黨的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n願終有一日我們的子孫能於煲底下相見，<br />\n毋忘初心。<br />\n願各位都可以在亂流下平安。"},{"pid":"a85d9235277cfdc3eeeef879327e1eb63a6dff55","tid":2426649,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"已變潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537257f1ad127f084c7297232114c47e95cb0c44","tid":2426649,"uid":250286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"293e7cb3a233492c7b2c7209f5258956aebb0a39","tid":2426649,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"0e2175ba7b80647ed0491c409b4422e95b60a885","tid":2426649,"uid":250286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4624c52a482b21ded781e7635802ea1c8f2f9fa7","tid":2426649,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"從來無忘記<br />\n<br />\n無論身處世界任何角落，都要記得自己係香港人"},{"pid":"08d0d5b21d66b684de3de030d51b1ac9e4a25c2f","tid":2426649,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:00:37.000Z","msg":"Never forget, never forgive."},{"pid":"500c3365d6d2cb7ed0dd4a0d98ae618d1210a707","tid":2426649,"uid":392446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食黃店抗爭從來沒有停止過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}